1
00:00:07,220 --> 00:00:11,820
♪She looks at the bright moon
hanging high above the clouds♪

2
00:00:11,860 --> 00:00:14,140
♪And I fall into the mountains♪

3
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:16,100
♪Protect this broken world♪

4
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:20,620
♪A faint wish♪

5
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:23,900
♪Life is just a dream,
isn't the world so?♪

6
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:27,620
♪Looking back,
I count the joys of my remaining years♪

7
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:31,020
♪It's difficult to see you in my dreams♪

8
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,940
♪Ignoring the coldness of the world,
I still linger♪

9
00:00:33,980 --> 00:00:37,300
♪Love and hate are intertwined,
not just in the past♪

10
00:00:37,340 --> 00:00:40,900
♪The past is painful,
and time goes by in a flash♪

11
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:44,500
♪Stars fall on the mountain top again♪

12
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:48,140
♪My heart is as pure as the moon
and connected to you♪

13
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:56,980
[No One But You]

14
00:00:56,980 --> 00:00:57,800
[Episode 6]

15
00:00:57,800 --> 00:01:01,980
[Let's find out which is tougher,
my heart or your life.]

16
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:04,780
Huan!

17
00:01:10,620 --> 00:01:11,500
Threatening me?

18
00:01:12,180 --> 00:01:13,500
Are you gambling with your life,

19
00:01:13,980 --> 00:01:14,980
and hoping I'll show mercy?

20
00:01:16,820 --> 00:01:17,860
How could that be the case?

21
00:01:18,780 --> 00:01:20,220
I'm not that important to you.

22
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:22,660
I'm just

23
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:24,340
proposing a trade.

24
00:01:25,100 --> 00:01:27,260
One life for another.

25
00:01:27,540 --> 00:01:28,340
Very well.

26
00:01:29,820 --> 00:01:30,980
Let's find out

27
00:01:31,260 --> 00:01:32,780
which is tougher,

28
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:34,780
my heart or your life.

29
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:38,060
Don't bully the other girls.

30
00:01:38,540 --> 00:01:40,860
I have paid the favors that I owed you.

31
00:01:49,460 --> 00:01:50,660
It seems

32
00:01:50,660 --> 00:01:52,420
my life is still a bit tougher.

33
00:01:56,260 --> 00:01:58,060
Your life was saved by me.

34
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:02,180
Whether you live or die, it's up to me.

35
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:09,140
Yudie!

36
00:02:09,140 --> 00:02:10,180
Qinghuan.

37
00:02:11,860 --> 00:02:12,700
Yudie!

38
00:02:18,220 --> 00:02:19,060
Why?

39
00:02:20,020 --> 00:02:21,700
Why did you hurt the innocent again?

40
00:02:22,060 --> 00:02:23,140
Don't be impatient.

41
00:02:23,780 --> 00:02:25,780
You still have some value left.

42
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:28,300
I'll wait, then.

43
00:02:33,420 --> 00:02:34,580
The body is there.

44
00:02:35,420 --> 00:02:37,540
You know what to do.

45
00:02:43,700 --> 00:02:45,580
Qinghuan is none of your concern.

46
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:47,300
You'd better stay away from her.

47
00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:49,060
Unfortunately,

48
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:51,260
my concern lies solely with Qinghuan.

49
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:53,420
All else is irrelevant.

50
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:56,580
You have ten seconds

51
00:02:56,580 --> 00:02:57,780
to depart with your followers.

52
00:02:58,220 --> 00:03:00,460
Otherwise, I'll kill them one by one.

53
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:07,260
Since both sides are present,

54
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:09,380
why delay?

55
00:03:09,820 --> 00:03:11,500
Let's have a fight today.

56
00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:12,340
Stop it!

57
00:03:12,860 --> 00:03:14,060
Here is Joys of Life,

58
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:15,740
not your battlefield.

59
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,140
Guests should abide by the host's rules.

60
00:03:19,660 --> 00:03:20,620
I guess this is it.

61
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:32,540
Everybody, behold.

62
00:03:33,100 --> 00:03:34,540
In collusion with the Spark Society,

63
00:03:34,860 --> 00:03:36,260
in opposition to the Military Governor's Mansion,

64
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:38,100
this is what you'll get.

65
00:03:44,340 --> 00:03:44,900
Sir,

66
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:48,940
there is something wrong with Yudie.

67
00:03:49,380 --> 00:03:51,260
She's a spy
for the Japanese Chamber of Commerce.

68
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:55,050
[File: Yudie]

69
00:03:59,140 --> 00:04:01,540
Placing spies around me

70
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:04,020
is like asking for death.

71
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:09,980
You've gone to great lengths for Miss Yu.

72
00:04:09,980 --> 00:04:10,740
That's truly brilliant.

73
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:15,740
Thank you for helping me today.

74
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:18,340
As long as it's your matter,

75
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:19,820
I will do my utmost to help.

76
00:04:19,820 --> 00:04:21,100
I am serious.

77
00:04:29,860 --> 00:04:31,100
Regarding my sister's death,

78
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:32,860
I have found some clues.

79
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:34,180
Could you...?

80
00:04:34,180 --> 00:04:34,900
No problem.

81
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:36,180
I will never say no

82
00:04:36,180 --> 00:04:37,300
to your matter.

83
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:04,340
Still angry about Yudie's death?

84
00:05:07,860 --> 00:05:08,700
I've said

85
00:05:09,820 --> 00:05:11,300
nobody was innocent.

86
00:05:13,140 --> 00:05:14,180
How dare I?

87
00:05:14,940 --> 00:05:16,500
Mohan is decisive and ruthless,

88
00:05:16,740 --> 00:05:18,380
If I say something improper,

89
00:05:18,780 --> 00:05:20,660
maybe the one
who dies tomorrow will be me.

90
00:05:23,300 --> 00:05:24,900
Did you mean it?

91
00:05:25,940 --> 00:05:27,820
Does it matter?

92
00:05:28,220 --> 00:05:30,020
From now on,
whatever you say will be taken as truth.

93
00:05:30,340 --> 00:05:31,220
I am not important at all.

94
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:55,180
Sir,

95
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:56,700
It seems like a tire has burst.

96
00:05:58,900 --> 00:05:59,700
Go down and check.

97
00:06:00,340 --> 00:06:00,700
Yes.

98
00:06:08,860 --> 00:06:11,380
How did you stop the car?

99
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:17,380
I want to go out for some fresh air.

100
00:06:19,020 --> 00:06:19,580
OK.

101
00:06:22,740 --> 00:06:23,540
Let go of me.

102
00:06:24,260 --> 00:06:25,220
Don't ever touch me again.

103
00:06:25,580 --> 00:06:26,900
Why are you pushing me?

104
00:06:28,020 --> 00:06:28,940
This is all your fault.

105
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:29,780
Don't touch me!

106
00:06:29,780 --> 00:06:30,740
You are blocking my way.

107
00:06:42,940 --> 00:06:43,740
I will give you a hit.

108
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:47,060
Let me pass!

109
00:06:47,620 --> 00:06:48,100
Go away.

110
00:06:48,100 --> 00:06:48,700
Let me pass!

111
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:51,420
You've got some guts,

112
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:53,180
daring to act right under his nose.

113
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:56,220
The most dangerous method

114
00:06:56,380 --> 00:06:57,620
is the safest.

115
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,180
Then I can't be too far behind you.

116
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:07,260
How about sharing a meal together?

117
00:07:09,100 --> 00:07:11,700
Jiang Mohan killed the informant
before I could take any action.

118
00:07:11,980 --> 00:07:14,340
But there is one informant
he would never dare to kill.

119
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:16,260
You mean...

120
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:17,340
The Marshal.

121
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:18,100
Correct.

122
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:20,260
I need you to create a disturbance

123
00:07:20,260 --> 00:07:21,260
around the Marshal's residence

124
00:07:21,420 --> 00:07:22,980
to cover me
while I retrieve the telegram documents.

125
00:07:23,300 --> 00:07:23,900
And then,

126
00:07:24,940 --> 00:07:26,700
tie up the butler
of the Marshal's residence.

127
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:29,100
We'll meet at your Qing Gang
in the afternoon.

128
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:32,820
Move it away.

129
00:07:32,820 --> 00:07:33,820
Look at you and your car.

130
00:07:33,820 --> 00:07:35,340
You've damaged my car.

131
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:38,380
It was broken at first.

132
00:07:38,380 --> 00:07:39,340
How could it be possible?

133
00:07:40,340 --> 00:07:42,220
Mohan, have a taste.

134
00:08:00,020 --> 00:08:00,820
Miss Yu.

135
00:08:03,420 --> 00:08:05,540
This is Jiang Mohan's petition report.

136
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:07,700
He confessed
that he personally killed Yu Qingqiu.

137
00:08:11,340 --> 00:08:11,940
You should know

138
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:14,060
what I expect to hear from you.

139
00:08:14,780 --> 00:08:15,620
I won't say more

140
00:08:15,620 --> 00:08:17,860
coercive and enticing nonsense.

141
00:08:18,460 --> 00:08:20,540
Loyalty or survival,

142
00:08:20,940 --> 00:08:21,940
it's your call.

143
00:08:24,580 --> 00:08:25,340
One.

144
00:08:27,620 --> 00:08:28,420
Two.

145
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:32,140
I'll tell you.

146
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:34,660
Back then, Jiang Mohan served
as a commander

147
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:37,780
beneath the Grand Marshal's authority.

148
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:39,420
I want you to get close to this woman,

149
00:08:39,660 --> 00:08:41,020
and find out her identity.

150
00:08:42,620 --> 00:08:44,800
[Name: Yu Qingqiu]

151
00:08:48,820 --> 00:08:49,740
I've found out.

152
00:08:50,420 --> 00:08:52,140
She is a key member
of the Sparks Society.

153
00:08:52,660 --> 00:08:53,940
This is the content
she has been exchanging.

154
00:08:59,140 --> 00:09:01,060
You know what you're doing.

155
00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:03,180
After the mission is accomplished,

156
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:05,420
I will promote you
to be the military governor.

157
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:10,620
[Merchant Group Wharf]

158
00:09:10,620 --> 00:09:11,700
Mohan, here you are.

159
00:09:38,860 --> 00:09:39,740
Qingqiu,

160
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:42,180
I had suspected

161
00:09:42,180 --> 00:09:44,180
Jiang Mohan was the murderer.

162
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:47,340
But I didn't expect the pain

163
00:09:49,820 --> 00:09:52,580
would still be so heart-wrenching.

164
00:09:57,420 --> 00:09:59,500
He approached my sister
with malicious intent,

165
00:10:00,100 --> 00:10:01,500
deceived her emotions and took her life.

166
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:04,420
I became the apprentice of my enemy,

167
00:10:04,420 --> 00:10:06,500
and stayed by his side for five years.

168
00:10:07,620 --> 00:10:09,100
I even...

169
00:10:10,540 --> 00:10:12,060
I am sorry, Qingqiu.

170
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:15,460
It's not your fault.

171
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:19,020
He is ruthless and extremely ambitious.

172
00:10:26,820 --> 00:10:28,180
I swear,

173
00:10:28,820 --> 00:10:30,540
I will personally avenge my enemy.

174
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:32,260
If I break this vow,

175
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:34,140
may I be condemned to hell,

176
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:36,100
and suffer eternal punishment.

177
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:46,340
I'll be at your side,

178
00:10:47,100 --> 00:10:48,380
ready to strike when needed.

179
00:11:13,300 --> 00:11:16,100
[Beizhou Military Governor's Mansion]
Jiang Mohan, I demand blood for blood.

180
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:45,300
♪The waves♪

181
00:11:45,380 --> 00:11:49,580
♪When will you
stop looking through them?♪

182
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:53,620
♪Missed the time
when the sun was restored♪

183
00:11:53,700 --> 00:11:57,780
♪What else do you expect to like?♪

184
00:11:57,820 --> 00:12:00,540
♪I thought you were an angel♪

185
00:12:00,620 --> 00:12:02,840
♪An angel who watched over me♪

186
00:12:02,860 --> 00:12:05,900
♪And saw every side of me♪

187
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:08,540
♪Until reality is flooded♪

188
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:10,780
♪You become sensible♪

189
00:12:10,860 --> 00:12:15,340
♪You are finally
out of touch with reality♪

190
00:12:15,650 --> 00:12:18,180
♪I hear the mountains, the seas,
and the people♪

191
00:12:18,260 --> 00:12:20,220
♪All clamoring because of you♪

192
00:12:20,340 --> 00:12:22,300
♪Hiding in the cape after the rain♪

193
00:12:22,460 --> 00:12:24,740
♪I cannot hear you♪

194
00:12:24,780 --> 00:12:28,260
♪So I opened my arms one last time♪

195
00:12:28,420 --> 00:12:31,780
♪But you escaped through the gap♪

196
00:12:31,890 --> 00:12:34,100
♪I saw winters come and summers go♪

197
00:12:34,140 --> 00:12:36,260
♪And thought there was ample time♪

198
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:38,300
♪Cannot withstand the waves♪

199
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:40,400
♪But you always make me panic♪

200
00:12:40,460 --> 00:12:44,700
♪How ridiculous, making me learn♪

201
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:48,060
♪How much I am worth♪
